*** Adding structure to existing subsystem of Bibliotheca Opalica ***

1. Add structure name to NORMSTRUCTS variable in SysDefs file.
2. For Documentation:

   a) add structure name to <subsystem>.structures.names in
      doc/bibopalicaman/DOSFOP.
   b) Create file <structure>.config in doc/bibopalicaman/DOSFOP
      with template below.


*** Rebuilding documentation from development tree ***

1. Do `ocs' in <ocssrc>/doc/bibopalicaman to create HTML files.
2. Do make pkg.doc in <ocssrc> to copy HTML files to installation.


----------
Template for <structure>.config:

STRUCTURE
name = {<structure>}
OPTIONAL
